title: High On Fire - Luminiferous 2015
description:
Luminiferous is the seventh album by metal band High On Fire. The album was generally well received Exclaim called it "Heavy metal at its finest, Luminiferous is a brilliant, dynamic release, showcasing High on Fire's penchant for diverse, thoughtful songwriting and impeccable musicianship."
Track listing

    The Black Plot - 5:31
    Carcosa - 7:11
    The Sunless Years - 5:06
    Slave the Hive - 3:50
    The Falconist - 6:06
    The Dark Side of the Compass - 5:30
    The Cave - 7:40
    Luminiferous - 4:03
    The Lethal Chamber - 8:49

Personnel

High on Fire

    Matt Pike - guitars, vocals
    Jeff Matz - bass
    Des Kensel - drums

Additional Personnel

    Kurt Ballou - Producer
